core.overview: Thirty years after the events of the first film, a new blade runner, LAPD Officer K, unearths a long-buried secret that has the potential to plunge what's left of society into chaos. K's discovery leads him on a quest to find Rick Deckard, a former LAPD blade runner who has been missing for 30 years.
core.tagline: The key to the future is finally unearthed.
core.title: Blade Runner 2049

release_dates.note: Festival du nouveau cinema de Montreal
